{
  "text": "Test-retest reliability was evaluated for the stable group by using Intraclass Correlation Coefficient (ICC). ICC values closer to 1.0 indicate higher test-retest reliability [CITATION_1] . We hypothesized that the test-retest reliability would be excellent for the stable group which will lie between 0.7-0.9 [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
